data.description: Welcome home to this well-maintained two-story beauty! The home has been updated with new HVAC units, a newer roof, new siding as well as renovated kitchen and baths. Good-bye carpet and say hello to all new flooring throughout. Why not spend quality time in the family room, living room, formal dining room or enclosed patio, the choice is yours. Oh, and don't forget the master bedroom is your secluded oasis that features not one but two walk-in closets and a beautifully done ensuite. The yard has been a labor of love and features an active well to help with curb appeal without the extra costs. A MUST SEE!
